Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:32.16,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(338.667,335)}Akagi Shigeru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:39.21,default - cyan,,0,0,0,,誰の肩に止まるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:39.21,Default - white,,0,0,0,,Whose shoulder will it land upon
