Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.58,0:25:22.31,small - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638.4,76.751)}East Team:\NTen: {\c&H00FF00&}49000{\c&HFFFFFF&} Hiroyuki: {\c&H0000FF&}1000
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.69,0:25:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(423.467,384.657)}this is an expression of our determination
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.56,0:25:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(422.933,396.131)}Without averting our eyes from hard facts,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.99,0:25:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,embrace each crisis while moving forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.46,0:25:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Opening the way
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.78,0:25:38.00,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\s1}SanAnKou{\s0}\NChitoitsu\NChanta\NSanSyoku\NIttsu
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.68,0:25:42.68,Default - white,,0,0,0,,{\pos(435.2,394.084)}East Round 2
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.90,0:26:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(422.667,385.667)}An awful starting hand, well beyond saving
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.36,0:26:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If he discards a South wind, the hand will not continue
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.82,0:26:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you retreat from such a position?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.52,0:26:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.75,0:29:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that, the match is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.05,0:29:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What I just discarded was the 6th White Dragon !
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.05,0:29:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Head bump?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.42,0:29:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This White Dragon Hiroyuki discarded wasn't a White Dragon at all
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.65,0:29:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I declared Ron on
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.75,0:29:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the missing tile that discard was destined to be
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.92,0:30:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If there isn't a 5 Sou(bamboo) in that Mahjong case
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.55,0:30:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the point penalty KNOCKS YOU THE FUCK OUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.12,0:30:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This swapped tile
